member.remarks:
Sample request:

    [
        {
            "op": "add",
            "path": "/textPositive",
            "value": "sample text"
        }
    ]
Don't forget to add "Content-Type": "application/json-patch+json". 

You need to have an User role to perform this action.

Sample request:

    [
        {
            "op": "add",
            "path": "/path",
            "value": "../../../Content/Images/Hotels/new-hotel-photo.jpeg"
        }
    ]
Don't forget to add "Content-Type": "application/json-patch+json". 

You need to have an Admin or HotelOwner role to perform this action.

